Start application "Variety"
	- disable change wallpaper every x minutes
	- close the window
	- click on the taskbar icon and select Wallpaper selector
	- choose wallpaper
	- unselect the Wallpaper selector
	
	
Desktop settings
	- right click on the desktop 
	- select desktop settings
	- open the "icons" menu
	- turn off the Default Icons
	
Prefered Apps
	- select browser
	- select terminal
	- select file manager
	
Keyboard Shortcuts
	- am-conky-session = super+c
	- arcolinux-logout = super+q
	- calculator = super+k
	- catfish = Lctrl+space
	- exo-open --launch FileManager = super+f
	- exo-open --launch TerminalEmulator = super+return
	- exo-open --launch WebBrowser = super+w
	- geany = super+t
	- qbittorrent = super+b
	- xfce4-popup-whiskermenu = super+altL
	- xkill = super+esc
	
Windows Manager
	- close window = ctrl+backspace
	- toggle fullscreen = super+Rshift
	- tile window to the top = super+up
	- tile window to the bottom = super+dn
	- tile window to the left = super+left
	- tile window to the right = super+right
	- hide window (minimize) = super+m
		
